snippet.title: Vault of the Void - Trailer
snippet.description:
Vault of the Void: A roguelite card game where you craft your deck, swapping in and out cards as you progress, perfecting the ultimate combos. Upgrade & customize your cards with Void Stones, infusing them with new abilities to help defeat the insidious minions that stand between you and The Void.

Website: http://www.vaultofthevoid.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1135810/Vault_of_the_Void/
Reddit: http://www.reddit.com/r/vaultofthevoid
